				<div class="content">
					<h2><span class="font-semi-bold">Welcome</span> <span class="smaller">to the <span class="font-semi-bold">D</span>ialogue-<span class="font-semi-bold">B</span>ased <span class="font-semi-bold">A</span>rgumentation <span class="font-semi-bold">S</span>oftware, or short <span class="font-semi-bold">D-BAS</span></span></h2>
					<p class="lead">This novel discussions software will help you to discuss a problem or statement in a structured manner.<br><br>D-Bas offers a lot of advantages, here are a few of them:</p>
					<ul class="lead list">
						<li>Use the wisdom of the crowd</li>
						<li>Easy to use and very powerful</li>
						<li>Avoid redundancy created as known in normal forums</li>
						<li>Every argument and position will be connected logically to each other</li>
					</ul>
					<br>
					<p class="lead">This project is based on research of the graduation school Online-Participation, governmentally subsidised by the <a href="http://www.wissenschaft.nrw.de/forschung/fortschritt-nrw/inter-und-transdisziplinaeres-forschungsumfeld-schaffen/fortschrittskolleg-online-partizipation/" alt="Ministry of Innovation, Science and Research in North Rhine-Westphalia">Ministry of Innovation, Science and Research in North Rhine-Westphalia</a>.</p>
